{"serial": "43037", "department_serial": 39, "code": "IM7065", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Human Resource Management", "ch": "人力資源管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "授課老師：嚴國晉老師"}, "instructor": {"en": [], "ch": []}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "404"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 77, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "授課老師：嚴國晉老師", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在探討現今的人力資源管理，幫助學生建立紮實的基礎，涵蓋所有關鍵的人力資源職能。在當今的商業環境中，人力資本已成為各組織最重要的資產之一。因此，如何競爭人才、建立並運用人才資源，是組織為取得競爭優勢所面臨的挑戰之一。\n完成本課程後，您應能夠：\n•了解並辨識各主要的人力資源管理職能。\n•認識當今人力資源管理中的主要趨勢、機會及挑戰。\n•能夠更好地診斷策略性組織情境，並運用人力資源技術來解決相關問題。\n•掌握作為企業員工所需的基本人力資源實務技能。", "en": "“This course deals with today’s human resource management for students to acquire a strong ground in all key HR functions. In today’s business environment, human capital has become one of the most important assets for any organizations. So how to compete for talent and build and deploy talent resources is one of the challenges for organization to help gaining its competitive advantage. \nAfter completing this course, you should:\n- Be able to identify each of the major HRM functions.\n- Be able to recognize the major trends, opportunities, and challenges in today’s HRM.\n- Be better able to diagnose strategic organizational situation and adopt HR techniques to address the issues.\n- Be able to equip with the fundamental competencies in HR practices as an employee in business. “"}, "outline": {"ch": "“課程簡介\n第一章 HRM導論\n公平雇用法令\n第三章 HRM策略與績效\n第四章 工作分析與人才管理流程\n第五章 人力規劃與招募\n第六章 測驗與甄選\n第七章 面談\n演講\n期中考\n第八章 教育訓練\n第九章 績效管理與評估\n第十章 職涯管理與留才\n第十七章 全球HRM\n第十一章 建立策略薪酬計畫\n第十二章 績效酬賞與福利\n期末考“", "en": "“Introduction\nCh. 1 Introduction to HRM\nEqual opportunity and the law\nCh. 3 Human resource management strategy and performance\nCh. 4 Job analysis and talent management process\nCh. 5 Personnel planning ＆ recruiting\nCh. 6 Employee testing and selection\nCh. 7 Interviewing candidates\nInvited speech\nMidterm examination\nCh. 8 Training and developing employees\nCh. 9 Performance management and appraisal\nCh. 10 Managing careers and retention\nCh. 17 Managing global HRM\nCh. 11 Establishing strategic pay plans\nCh. 12 Pay for performance and benefits\nFinal exam“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“Dessler, G. Human Resource Management, 17th Edition? 2024 Pearson“", "en": "“Dessler, G. Human Resource Management, 17th Edition? 2024 Pearson“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席 10％\n課堂參與、作業 40％ \n期中考 25％\n期末考或報告 25％", "en": "Attendance 10％\nparticipation, assignment 40％\nmidterm examination 25％\nfinal examination 25％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "個別約定", "en": "by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "安排學生自主學習以上課中發表討論。", "en": "Arrange time slot for independent study and in class discussion"}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識", "en": "商管知識"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "原創性", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉其專業領域文獻", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Original Contribution", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Proficiency with Discipline-related Literature", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on p